# Repo Workflow Rules

- Use Supabase for database work. Do not introduce PostgreSQL-specific setup.
- Keep implementation MVP-level; avoid overengineering.
- Make small, feature-wise commits.
- Keep commit messages short and human-friendly.
- Use prefixes:
  - `[ADD] added ...`
  - `[FIX] fixed ...`
- Avoid AI-style long commit messages.
